summary: Hello! My name is Tobie Madsen. I was born in raised in Mesa, Arizona and recently graduated from Brigham Young University-Idaho with a B.A. in Visual Communication and a module in Public Relations. I have always possessed an overwhelming need to tell stories. As a child I would write short stories, as a teenager I would share stories on the stage, and now as an adult I continues to tell stories through my creative approach to marketing tactics and brand design. I am passionate about helping businesses expand their reach of influence through social media.  Let's connect!
